### ══════════════════════════════════════
###  AUTH
### ══════════════════════════════════════

### 1. 회원가입 (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "loginId": "testuser",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "nickname": "테스트유저"
}

### 2. 로그인 (POST)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "loginId": "yth1209",
    "password": "sd003124*"
}

### 3. 내 정보 조회 (GET) — JWT 필요
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}



### ══════════════════════════════════════
###  SERIES
### ══════════════════════════════════════

### 4. 전체 시리즈 목록 조회 (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/series

### 5. 내 시리즈 목록 조회 (GET) — JWT 필요
GET {{baseUrl}}/series/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 6. 시리즈 생성 (POST) — JWT 필요
# @name createSeries
POST {{baseUrl}}/series
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

{
    "title": "배신당한 화산파 삼류제자가 칼을 숨김",
    "description": "작품 소개 텍스트 (선택)"
}

### 7. 시리즈 상세 조회 (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/series/{{seriesId}}

### 8. 시리즈 에셋 조회 (GET) — 캐릭터·배경 S3 URL 반환
GET {{baseUrl}}/series/{{seriesId}}/assets



### ══════════════════════════════════════
###  EPISODE
### ══════════════════════════════════════

### 9. 회차 생성 (POST) — JWT 필요, multipart/form-data
# @name createEpisode
# file 첨부는 REST Client 확장에서 < 문법으로 지정
POST {{baseUrl}}/series/{{seriesId}}/episodes
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

1화 - 서막
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="episode1.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./episode1.txt
------Boundary--

### 10. 회차 상세 조회 (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/series/{{seriesId}}/episodes/{{episodeNumber}}

### 11. VN 스크립트 조회 (GET) — 비주얼 노벨 변환 결과
GET {{baseUrl}}/series/{{seriesId}}/episodes/{{episodeNumber}}/vn-script

### 12. 회차 삭제 (DELETE) — JWT 필요
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/series/{{seriesId}}/episodes/{{episodeNumber}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}



### ══════════════════════════════════════
###  PARSING  (파이프라인 Step 2~4)
### ══════════════════════════════════════

### 13. 캐릭터 파싱 (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/parsing/characters
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "seriesId": "{{seriesId}}",
    "episodeNumber": {{episodeNumber}}
}

### 14. 배경 파싱 (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/parsing/backgrounds
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "seriesId": "{{seriesId}}",
    "episodeNumber": {{episodeNumber}}
}

### 15. 씬 파싱 (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/parsing/scenes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "seriesId": "{{seriesId}}",
    "episodeNumber": {{episodeNumber}}
}



### ══════════════════════════════════════
###  IMAGE  (파이프라인 Step 5~6)
### ══════════════════════════════════════

### 16. 캐릭터 이미지 생성 (POST) — 백그라운드 실행
POST {{baseUrl}}/images/characters
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "seriesId": "{{seriesId}}"
}

### 17. 배경 이미지 생성 (POST) — 백그라운드 실행
POST {{baseUrl}}/images/backgrounds
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "seriesId": "{{seriesId}}"
}
